        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This foul-smelling pink paste is traditionally kept in a tightly sealed jar. Spreading the salve on exposed skin grants an item bonus to saving throws against all afflictions that have the fungus trait or that originate from creatures with the fungus trait. The bonus lasts for 6 hours.",
